column5: Sure Im a super genius with Warlock powers that I cant even comprehend but if you saw my post about PCG puts it all in perspective There are just stocks that you dont trade well and you should just forget about and move on but then theres the revenge factor If you just go back one more time and make some money you promise to stop going near it and then it burns you again Thats PCG to me Hardest thing in trading is owning up to your struggles and finding a work around Swallow your pride and check the ego some stocks just own you Deal with it and leave them alone Why waste time with the losers when you can go back to the winner like BYND which weve been on the right side of since it came out You dont see me mentioning BABA and SQ anymore do ya Since the buy and holds on both that worked out nicely each last yr they have proved to be untradeable So I dont and dont
